課程概述 Course Description
       本課程教授燃燒理論，理論分析各式燃燒火焰，並輔以實驗現象，說明闡述其物理意義。This course describes combustion theory, analytically introduces various burning flames incorporated with experimental observations, and explains their physical meaning.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
本課程教授燃燒理論，理論分析各式燃燒火焰，並輔以實驗現象，說明闡述其物理意義。培育創新思考與獨立研究之能力培育解決問題與協調整合之能力 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Conservation Equations2Conservation Equations3Heat and Mass Transfer without Chemical Reaction4Heat and Mass Transfer without Chemical Reaction5Combustion Waves in Premixtures6Combustion Waves in Premixtures7Deflagration Waves in Premixtures8Deflagration Waves in Premixtures9Diffusion Flames10Diffusion Flames11Jet Diffusion Flames12Jet Diffusion Flames13Droplet Vaporization and Combustion14Droplet Vaporization and Combustion15Flame Stretch and Preferential Diffusion on Laminar Flames16Flame Stretch and Preferential Diffusion on Laminar Flames17Ignition and Extinction Phenomena18Ignition and Extinction Phenomena 

